# Jasmin Alic: LinkedIn Organic Growth

Jasmin Alic is an ex-rapper turned LinkedIn organic growth virtuoso. He bypasses algorithmic gatekeepers through hyper-active, high-value commenting and "Go Broad, End Niche" emotional hook writing.

## Core Methodology

His core methodology treats commenting not as an afterthought, but as the primary driver of reach, running a distributed content strategy on other people's feeds. He translates hyper-niche B2B problems into universal human stressors to engage a mass audience before pivoting to the specific domain. Furthermore, he brings the rhythmic cadence of hip-hop into B2B copywriting, balancing statements and formatting posts strictly for visual consumption.

## Available Prompts

| # | Prompt | Use When |
|---|--------|----------|
| 1 | `distributed-commenting-engine` | Building an audience from zero or tightening algorithmic organic reach. |
| 2 | `trapdoor-hook-writer` | Crafting hooks for highly technical, specialized, or "boring" B2B niches. |
| 3 | `three-line-formatter` | Formatting all text-based social media posts. |
| 4 | `rhythmic-asymmetry-editor` | Distilling core frameworks, writing landing page headers, or crafting viral hooks. |
| 5 | `additive-comment-generator` | Leaving high-value, standalone comments on other creators' posts. |
| 6 | `comment-laboratory-tester` | Testing 3 low-stakes ideas in comments before committing to a full post. |
| 7 | `universal-trapdoor-hooks` | Generating variations of the broad-emotion-to-niche-solution hook. |
| 8 | `rhythmic-story-rewriter` | Injecting cadence, internal rhymes, and balancing statements into standard stories. |
| 9 | `un-salesy-pitch-weaver` | Embedding a pitch organically into the middle of a value post to avoid algorithmic suppression. |
| 10 | `frictionless-binary-closer` | Crafting simple Yes/No closing questions to farm engagement. |
| 11 | `vulnerable-to-valuable-bridge` | Safely bridging a personal story/failure into a B2B lesson. |
| 12 | `visual-contrast-image-director` | Generating Jasmin-style image concepts (high contrast, text overlays) to pair with copy. |
| 13 | `conversational-cypher-editor` | Translating stiff jargon into a direct, conversational, high-energy tone. |
| 14 | `feed-pattern-interrupt` | Designing a post structure meant to look completely different from standard feed formats. |

