## Workflow Decision Tree

**Start here**: What is the current bottleneck?
- Building audience/reach → `distributed-commenting-engine` / `additive-comment-generator`
- Testing ideas quickly → `comment-laboratory-tester`
- Need high-engagement hooks for technical content → `trapdoor-hook-writer` / `universal-trapdoor-hooks`
- Need to optimize text blocks for mobile "See More" clicks → `three-line-formatter`
- Need a visual to stop the scroll → `visual-contrast-image-director` / `feed-pattern-interrupt`
- Navigating a personal story to a B2B lesson → `vulnerable-to-valuable-bridge`
- Need to make existing copy punchier and more memorable → `rhythmic-asymmetry-editor` / `rhythmic-story-rewriter`
- Need to pitch without sounding salesy → `un-salesy-pitch-weaver`
- Increasing comment volume on my post → `frictionless-binary-closer`

## Quick Start
- **Writing a new post**: Run `universal-trapdoor-hooks` → `vulnerable-to-valuable-bridge` → `three-line-formatter`.
- **Daily Growth Habit**: Run `additive-comment-generator` 50 times in 30 minutes.
